ITEM NO.7                  COURT NO.11                  SECTION XII
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
Petition for Special Leave to Appeal (C) No. 15834/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated 09-04-2025
in WAMD No. 2282/2024 passed by the High Court of Judicature at
Madras at Madurai]
S. BYJU NIZETH PAAUL                               Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
THE DIRECTOR OF COLLEGIATE EDUCATION & ORS.        Respondent(s)
(IA No. 149779/2025 - WITHDRAWAL OF CASE / APPLICATION)
 
Date : 04-07-2025 This matter was called on for hearing today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE M.M. SUNDRESH
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE K. VINOD CHANDRAN
(PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH)
For Petitioner(s) : 
                   Mr. Nachiketa Joshi, Sr. Adv.
                   Mr. Abhijeet Sinha, AOR
                   Mr. Sarthak Gaurav, Adv.
                   Ms. Rimmi Bharadwaj, Adv.                      
For Respondent(s) : 
                   Ms. Merlyn Rachel J., AOR
                   Mr. Martin Jaykumar, Adv.
                   Mr. Balaji, Adv.
                   Mr. Bharathi Rajan S., Adv.                   
                   
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
I.A. No. 149779/2025 for withdrawal of the present Special
Leave Petition is allowed.
The Special Leave Petition is dismissed as withdrawn.
However, all the issues and questions raised by both the sides
including the question of maintainability, are left open.
(DEEPAK GUGLANI)                                 (POONAM VAID)
   AR-cum-PS                               ASSISTANT REGISTRAR
